OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1784638109
OL,3,CDrug dealer who killed charity cyclist
OL,4,Cin crash jailed
OL,6,FA drug dealer has been jailed for more
OL,7,Fthan a decade after killing a cyclist
OL,8,Fwho was training for a charity cycle
OL,9,Fride.
OL,11,FSohail Jahangir, 23, crashed into 59-
OL,12,Fyear-old Adrian Stokes as cycled along
OL,13,FDenton Road, between Ilkley and Otley
OL,14,Fin West Yorkshire.
OL,16,FMr Stokes was training for an event to
OL,17,Fhelp underprivileged young people in
OL,18,FBradford when the incident happened on
OL,19,F2 April 2023.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
