FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1784638109
OL,3,CDrug dealer who killed charity cyclist
OL,4,Cin crash jailed
OL,6,FJahangir, of Woodview, Bradford,
OL,7,Fadmitted causing death by dangerous
OL,8,Fdriving along with drug dealing and a
OL,9,Fseparate dangerous driving charge.
OL,11,FHe was jailed for 10 years and seven
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,FBradford Crown Court heard Mr Stokes
OL,15,Fwas turning right near Denton Bridge
OL,16,Fwhen Jahangir overtook another car in
OL,17,Fhis Audi Q2 and collided with him.
OL,19,FHe died at the scene.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
