PN,33903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1784638109
OL,3,CDrug dealer who killed charity cyclist
OL,4,Cin crash jailed
OL,6,FIn a statement, Mr Stokes' wife said:
OL,7,F"He was enjoying the beautiful
OL,8,Fcountryside he loved so much on that
OL,9,Fsunny afternoon.
OL,11,F"But he never came home. In that
OL,12,Fmoment our lives were shattered."
OL,14,FDet Con Richard Grey, of North
OL,15,FYorkshire Police, said: "Adrian set
OL,16,Fout that day to get some training for
OL,17,Fa charity event he was taking part in
OL,18,Fand was doing nothing wrong.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,340,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F339A1784638109
OL,3,CDrug dealer who killed charity cyclist
OL,4,Cin crash jailed
OL,6,F"He was riding along, using the road
OL,7,Fin a responsible and safe manner as
OL,8,Fwas described by the witness who also
OL,9,Fdid exactly the right thing by slowing
OL,10,Fand allowing him space to turn right.
OL,12,F"The one who did not do the right
OL,13,Fthing was Sohail Jahangir. His actions
OL,14,Fhave caused this tragedy and from that
OL,15,Fday onward will have lasting effects
OL,16,Fon all who have been involved."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/4
